videos.description: Off the steal, Ismael Sanogo runs the break and dishes to Myles Powell for a layup.
videos.headline: Seton Hall's Powell, Sanogo combine for a fast break layup

videos.description: Myles Powell drives the lane and scores an right-handed layup for Seton Hall.
videos.headline: Gold at the rim for Powell and the Pirates.

videos.description: Angel Degado beats the triple team with over-the-head pass to Ismael Sanogo who scores a left-handed layup.
videos.headline: Delgado beats triple team to set up bucket

videos.description: Seton Hall's Desi Rodriguez shakes and bakes St. Peter's Nnamdi Enechionyia and buries a jumper in the first half.

videos.headline: St. Peters' Griffin hits 3-pointer in transition

videos.headline: Seton Hall's Cale shows off the hops for dunk
